<plot>A young elephant's parents disappear while sailing. The distraught youngster is at home when the comic and jovial Uncle Elephant arrives to collect him. The uncle and his nephew pass the time in myriad ways while awaiting the return of the lost parents. Eventually the parents do return, after the little elephant has developed a warm and fun relationship with his uncle.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?628892</url></doc>
